1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:04,000
Also, ich wurde in Berlin geboren.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,500
In neunzehnhundertdreiundzwanzig.

3
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:10,000
My father was a businessman.

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,500
Er hatte ein Geschäft in der Stadt.

5
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,000
We lived there until 1938.

6
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,500
♪♪

7
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:22,000
Dann mussten wir nach Amerika gehen.

8
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,500
Because of the political situation.

9
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:29,000
Es war sehr schwierig für uns.

10
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:32,500
I was only fifteen years old.

11
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:35,000
[PAUSE]

12
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,500
Meine Mutter weinte jeden Tag.

13
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:42,000
She missed her homeland terribly.

14
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,500
Aber wir hatten keine andere Wahl.

15
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:49,000
We had to adapt to our new life.

16
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:52,500
In die Wehrmacht gekommen?

17
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:56,000
No, I was too young then.

18
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:59,500
Aber mein älterer Bruder, ja.

19
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:03,000
He served from 1940 to 1943.

20
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:06,500
Er war bei der Luftwaffe.